    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Halflings are often seen as fearless, but some are instead particularly cautious. Halflings with this species trait gain a +1 bonus to Initiative checks and to melee attack rolls (+3 total) when flanking. When affected by a fear effect, their land speed increases by 10 feet and they gain a +1 bonus to AC.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces surefooted and halfling luck.</strong></p>\n<p><strong></strong></p><strong></strong><p><strong></strong><em>Toggle on/off speed increase and AC bonus while affected by a Fear effect in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
    },
